火箭專家赫爾曼&middot;奧伯特有一個想法，用火箭把一面直徑超過1.5公里的「鏡子」送到跟地球同步的軌道上。它可以聚焦太陽光，並釋放出巨大能量，足以摧毀世界上任何一座城市，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">甚至摧毀地球</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/military/qo2q6g.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fmilitary%2Fqo2q6g.html&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c44d4cb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/military/qo2q6g.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ultimatemark.com/gundam/images/sm13_salamis04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ultimatemark.com%2Fgundam%2Fimages%2Fsm13_salamis04.jpg&h=de8e6864&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a055e48213818781837298b597b33085dd31b6","tid":201870,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:46:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真北韓軍備衰極都有70年代水平既。<br />\n不過講士氣軍心民心呢d就有得拗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但德國係1940年吞併法國 橫掃歐陸<br />\n而家既北韓人民軍食都食唔飽wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662299a00490d019523fba78e8363e9b010fe262","tid":201870,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講真北韓軍備衰極都有70年代水平既。<br />\n不過講士氣軍心民心呢d就有得拗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但德國係1940年吞併法國 橫掃歐陸<br />\n而家既北韓人民軍食都食唔飽wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊撚個同你講北韓軍隊食唔飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起碼最精銳個20%一定食得飽先 <br />\n大飢荒過咗 就算係餓都只係部分軍人同大部分人民"},{"pid":"757830fbca5c9d83f8f4c9e951d9b449eb65203d","tid":201870,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"